title: TUESDAY 5/25 - AARON RODGERS SPEAKS OUT
itunes:title: TUESDAY 5/25 - AARON RODGERS SPEAKS OUT
description:
Packers QB Aaron Rodgers (0:06) finally speaks about his situation with the Packers. Broncos QB Drew Lock (0:54) addresses his future in Denver, as does his teammate Von Miller (1:39). Deshaun Watson (2:38) a no-show in Houston. Julio Jones' (2:58) time in Atlanta could be coming to an end, while Matthew Stafford (3:21) looks forward to his time with the Rams. Plus, Derwin James (4:03) back on the field for the Chargers
